    "title": "Distribution Manager Vacancy at CMA CGM India - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "Join the CMA CGM India family as a Distribution Manager in Jodhpur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout CMA CGM India:\nCMA CGM India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with CMA CGM India!",
